    <li>
        
        <h3 class="beetle">
            <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/9E4E086CC9EE03D0F196A1FAE30AFF9123A8A0A6/1998894.png" alt="Roller Beetle" style="width:50px;" />
            <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Roller_Beetle" target="_blank">Roller Beetle</a>
        </h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Unlock: <span class="pof">Path of Fire: Living World Story 4</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                Masteries: <span class="pof">Path of Fire: Living World Story 4</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                Combat Mount: NO
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    The roller beetle is a great mount if you have a long distance to cover and relatively flat land to traverse, having the ability to go just as fast as the griffon.
                    The <span class="beetle">Roller Beetle's</span> biggest weakness is running into objects and losing all of its momentum.
                    If you don't have any energy to get back up to speed, the <span class="beetle">Roller Beetle</span> is slower than even the turtle.
                    Don't hesitate to use Bond of Vigor to regain your endurance quickly.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        
        <h3 class="griffon">
            <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/0307F624D93C09236934C3CEE63063CD1C96ACAB/1822130.png" alt="Griffon" style="width:50px;" />
            <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Griffon" target="_blank">Griffon</a>
        </h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Unlock: <span class="pof">Path of Fire</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                Masteries: <span class="pof">Path of Fire</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                Combat Mount: NO
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    You must complete the entire <span class="pof">Path of Fire</span> story to unlock the 
                    <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Griffon#Unlocking" target="_blank">questline</a>
                    for the <span class="griffon">Griffon</span>.
                    This quest will take 250 Gold to complete.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The <span class="griffon">Griffon</span> is your fastest mount, given you have enough height to get up to speed with a dive.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        
    </li>
    <li>
        <h3 class="skyscale">
            <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/461C02AE745D07C69EC2FBC1AE10E140D8E3E96B/2140530.png" alt="Skyscale" style="width:50px;" />
            <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Skyscale" target="_blank">Skyscale</a>
        </h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Unlock: <span class="pof">Path of Fire: Living World Story 4</span> || <span class="soto">Secrets of the Obscure</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                Masteries: <span class="pof">Path of Fire: Living World Story 4</span> & <span class="soto">Secrets of the Obscure</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                Combat Launch: 3min CD, mount your <span class="skyscale">Skyscale</span> while in combat!
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    The <span class="skyscale">Skyscale</span> is extremely versatile, having the highest vertical and able to fly. 
                    The <span class="skyscale">Skyscale</span> can move upward from a standstill, even higher than the <span class="springer">Springer</span>.
                    It can also cling to walls and boost upward, allowing you to scale very high walls with ease.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
